		<description><![CDATA[There really must be a murder, or at least a major felony &#8212; otherwise, what&#8217;s the point? Who&#8217;s ripping off the hand towels at the Dorchester Hotel is hardly the business of a mystery novel. Howard Haycraft]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>There really must be a murder, or at least a major felony &#8212; otherwise, what&#8217;s the point? Who&#8217;s ripping off the hand towels at the Dorchester Hotel is hardly the business of a mystery novel.</p>
<p style="padding-left: 330px;">Howard Haycraft</p>
